Name: Shining Star
Desc: Appears after making a 5-ping in a straight line or cross.\nSwap or double tap to dissolve 12 random Signal Orbs and attack all summoned units once.

Name: Vertical Slash
Desc: Appears after making a 5-ping in a T-shape.\nSwap or double tap to dissolve the column it belongs to.

Name: Blast
Desc: Appears after making a 5-ping in an L-shape.\nSwap or double tap to dissolve a 3x3 area around it.

Name: Rapid Fire
Desc: Appears after making a 4-ping.\nSwap or double tap to dissolve 4 random Signal Orbs.
